Rating: 2
Adding chorizo is a nice change from traditional fried rice recipes. Add some egg by scrambling two eggs in a bowl and moving the rice aside. Mix the egg to the rice. Chorizo is a traditional meat additive to egg recipes. Spicy and different. I will make it again using different ingrediants for variety.

